## 🚀 How to Run the App

The development server is already running. Simply:

1. Open your browser
2. Navigate to: **http://localhost:5173/**
3. The app will load automatically

### If you need to restart the server:

```bash
cd e:\Working\Protoverse\protoverse-app
npm run dev
```

