## 🎨 Design System Highlights

### Color Palette
- **Primary Blue:** #4A90E2 (Calming, trustworthy)
- **Secondary Teal:** #5DADE2 (Healing, balanced)
- **Success Green:** #6FCF97 (Growth, hope)
- **Warning Orange:** #F6AD55 (Attention without panic)
- **Crisis Red:** #E53E3E (Emergency only)

### Typography
- **Primary Font:** Inter (UI elements)
- **Secondary Font:** Lora (Headings, emotional content)
- **WCAG 2.1 AA compliant** for accessibility

### Design Philosophy
- ✅ Calm, not clinical
- ✅ Safe, not scary
- ✅ Simple, not simplistic
- ✅ Empathetic, not patronizing

