## 🎯 Deployment Options

### Option 1: Vercel (Recommended)
```bash
npm install -g vercel
vercel
```

### Option 2: Netlify
```bash
npm run build
# Drag & drop 'dist' folder to Netlify
```

### Option 3: GitHub Pages
```bash
npm install gh-pages -D
# Add to package.json:
# "homepage": "https://yourusername.github.io/protoverse-app"
# "deploy": "gh-pages -d dist"
npm run build
npm run deploy
```

---

