## 🆘 Troubleshooting

### Server won't start
```bash
# Kill existing process
taskkill /F /IM node.exe
# Restart
npm run dev
```

### Port 5173 already in use
```bash
# Change port in vite.config.js
export default {
  server: {
    port: 3000
  }
}
```

### Styles not loading
```bash
# Clear cache and restart
rm -rf node_modules
npm install
npm run dev
```

